title: If My Favorite Pop Idol Made It to the Budokan, I Would Die
subTitle: Eripiyo becomes obsessed with Maina from idol group ChamJam. She spends all her money on Maina's merchandise and works multiple jobs, while Maina worries about Eripiyo's extreme dedication.

title: Brightburn
subTitle: Tori and Kyle find a baby boy in a spaceship and adopt him as their own child, Brandon. However, after turning 12, Brandon learns that he has superpowers and begins to use them for sinister purposes.

title: Ghost Rider
subTitle: Motorcycle stuntman Johnny Blaze gives up his soul to save his father and becomes the Ghost Rider to fight against Blackheart, the son of Mephistopheles, the devil himself.

title: Hollow Man
subTitle: Sebastian Caine, a scientist, develops an invisibility serum. However, when he uses it on himself and is unable to reverse the effects, it results in horrifying consequences.

title: Bloodshot
subTitle: A soldier who died on duty is resurrected and given superhuman abilities by the RST Corp. But soon he realises the truth about his past and his resurrection and sets out to get revenge.

title: Vantage Point
subTitle: An unknown sniper attempts to assassinate the President of the United States during a tour in Spain and a handful of individuals close to the event recount it from their unique perspectives.

title: XXX
subTitle: The US government recruits extreme sports athlete Xander Cage to infiltrate a Russian criminal ring, which is plotting the destruction of the world.

subTitle: Tintin's new model ship sparks an adventure of intrigue and theft. He uncovers a historical mystery involving treasure, rival groups and a quest for scrolls revealing a sunken ship's location.

title: Bad Boys for Life
subTitle: Ageing bad boys Mike Lowrey and Marcus Burnett manoeuvre midlife crises, high-speed chases, and explosive collisions with an enemy who can set the world on fire to avenge Benito.

subTitle: Curtis and his family are asked to install an artificial intelligence program in their house in a bid to test it. However, they soon begin to experience disturbing occurrences.

subTitle: Miles Morales begins his new life as Spider-Man after receiving a spider bite. However, things take a strange twist when he meets alternate versions of himself from other universes.

title: Bad Boys II

subTitle: A team of researchers is in Borneo to find the blood orchid, a flower that could hold the secret to eternal life. However, the scientists run afoul of the jungle's deadly snakes.
